Package madkitgroupextension.kernel

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GroupChangementNotifier
    This interface is used by internal processes of MadKitGroupExtension.
    MKGEAbstractAgent
    This is the common interface of each MadKitGroupExtension agent (AbstractAgent, Agent, Scheduler, Watcher, SwingViewer).
    MKGEAgent
    This is the common interface for the next MadKitGroupExtension agents : Agent, Scheduler.
    MKGEScheduler
    This is the common interface for the next MadKitGroupExtension agents : Scheduler.
    MKGESwingViewer
    This is the common interface for the next MadKitGroupExtension agents : SwingViewer.
    MKGEWatcher
    This is the common interface for the next MadKitGroupExtension agents : Watcher, SwingViewer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAgent
    The class AbstractAgent of MadKitGroupExtension inherits from the class AbstractAgent of MadKit.
    AbstractGroup
    MadKitGroupExtension aims to encapsulate MadKit in order to extends the agent/group/role principle by giving the possibility to the user to work with a hierarchy of groups.
    Activator<A extends AbstractAgent & MKGEAbstractAgent>
    The class Activator of MadKitGroupExtension has the same role of the class Activator of MadKit.
    Agent  
    Group
    MadKitGroupExtension aims to encapsulate MadKit in order to extends the agent/group/role principle by giving the possibility to the user to work with a hierarchy of groups.
    GroupRole  
    MadKitGroupExtension
    The class MadKitGroupExtension inherits from the class MadKit.
    MultiGroup
    MadKitGroupExtension aims to encapsulate MadKit in order to extends the agent/group/role principle by giving the possibility to the user to work with a hierarchy of groups.
    Probe<A extends AbstractAgent & MKGEAbstractAgent>
    The class Probe of MadKitGroupExtension seems like the class Probe of MadKit.
    Role
    This class enables to encapsulate a role and a group (and its community).
    Scheduler

    The class Watcher of MadKitGroupExtension inherits from the class Watcher of MadKit.
